  guid: e11dcad1-28b3-4a4a-a5cc-66f913b47bbe
  itemName: Note #4
  description: "Boss,\r\n\r\nThe last piece is secured in the northeast section.
    It\u2019s been stashed out of sight, same as the others.\r\n\r\nMoretti, Bellini,
    and Caruso are stationed there, keeping watch. Three on it\u2014no one gets close
    without them knowing.\r\n\r\nThe pieces remain separated. Still no risk of them
    being brought together.\r\n\r\nWe\u2019ll hold position and wait for your word.\r\n"
  icon: {fileID: 7509403117698529453, guid: 945f2a5ccec718842a0f13fe94a2b967, type: 3}
